=== Janan island ===
Janan island, a small island south of Hawar island, was also considered in the 2001 {{abbr|ICJ|International Court of Justice}} judgment. Based on a previous agreement when both Qatar and Bahrain were under British protection, it was judged to be separate from the Hawar islands and so considered by the court separately.<ref name=icj54 /> It was awarded to Qatar.<ref name=icj81 />
